Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よく分からない機械はともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:40.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こういう所は結構綺麗だね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:43.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと閉じてたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:50.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな場所なら　何か昔のことでも分かったりするのかなと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:53.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔のことって　例えば？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:58.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の人々がどんな暮らしをしていたのか…とか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,服とか言葉とかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:03.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでそんなこと知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういえば　ヌコがいないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:18.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　たまにどっか行くよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,また爆弾か何か食べてるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:25.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,気になる？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:29.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たまにさ　誰かと会って三人になったりするじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:32.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,イシイとかカナザワに会ったり？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:37.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌコもそうだけど　少し違う雰囲気になるなーと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,賑やかというか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人だけだと寂しい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:44.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんは寂しい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:49.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　少しは　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いてっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この入れ物の感じはまさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いてててて…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれの匂いがする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:03.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:07.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:12.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫かな　なんか黒いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べられるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:16.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べられる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:27.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,う…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これってあの味だよね　チョコの味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,甘い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:43.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べ物のことはよく覚えているんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:51.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしかして　これがチョコなのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　チョコ味の何かでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:55.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:04.11,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　ある意味それも昔のことなのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,味も情報だなと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　記録できないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい　チー…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:18.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかカメラに文字が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,接続できる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　ヌコ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:48.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　これ私たちが撮った写真だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:52.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カメラの中身を映しているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,空中に？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな機能が…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　見て　懐かしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,懐かしいっていうほど前じゃないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは何だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この写真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちが撮ったやつじゃないね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お　地図の人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カナザワな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,と…隣りにいる女の人は？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:33.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この辺の写真　カナザワが撮ったのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちと会った時は一人だったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.71,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,フォルダ　たくさんある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,フォルダ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部見よう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっ　ちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:06.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい　人がいっぱいいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:11.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これ…全部カメラの中に入ってたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えーそれでは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,動いた　喋った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ど…動画っていうやつかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,機械進化論研究会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,第十二回報告を始めます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:34.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,撮れてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,オッケーオッケー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えー　今回のサンプルはこの小型機械です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:46.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちはこの機械　十七番乙種と名付けました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:52.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この種は生産設備に対し　あるプログラムを注入することにより
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,強制的に自らを増殖します
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちと同じくらいの歳の女の子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.26,TEXT-JP-UP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,このような複雑な
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:03.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,プロセスが変異と淘汰で生まれることは考えづらく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこは進化でいいよねってことになったじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,人の設計にしては利己的すぎるって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.31,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ？そうだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこ大事なとこじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:19.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:26.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでちーちゃんが昔のこと知りたがるのか　少し分かったかも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの…私お腹すいた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たち　ずっと二人っきりだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:48.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こうして人々が暮らしてたんだなってことが分かると
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほーらミドリ　パパだぞー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,パパのこと嫌いって言ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:20.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだその口の利き方は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめなさいって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,パンチ　おいでー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,本日　隣国に宣戦布告し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:39.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　もう一度意見調整してから報告するということで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,言ってないだろ　そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大規模な空襲が…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　パパのせいだよー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:08.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我が軍は大勝利を収め　隣国の死者は五億人を超える
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,というわけで　ポテトを買ってきましたー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたってさー　意外と食い意地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,電磁波爆弾の使用を通告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すべての電子機器はその機能が失われ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.11,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,一着はミキちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,Happy bir…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,各都市　各階層との通信が途絶し
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:58.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,主よ　あなたの下に召された兄弟と共に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,永久の喜びを分かち合えますように
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,少しだけ寂しくない気がするね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,配管置き場を抜けられるのはお前たちぐらいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,上に登りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:40.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人なら少ない食料で長く生きられる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おじいさんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く行きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌコはまたいないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:14.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれはどういう生き物なんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,扉を開けたり　機械を操作したり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:23.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,受信機を通して会話するし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　どうでもいいかー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いたいた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　どこに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかデカくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,デカイ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　ヌコ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしよう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お…追いかけなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も私を食べるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:36.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの受信機がないと喋れないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前はあのデカイやつと会話できないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつにユーを吐き出してくれって頼めないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私の言ってること分かる？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:11.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前はまだ小さいだけで　本当は人間の敵なのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,敵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,敵ってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:10.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.71,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今行くから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユーがいなくなったら　私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？食べられたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか頑張ったら出れた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,頑張ったって…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:10.01,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は生きている人間を食べたりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつが喋っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は発声器官を持たないが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:20.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,音波を言語として解読することができる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから　この船の設備を利用している
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,幼体は通信範囲が狭いせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,稀にそういうことが起きる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:55.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは我々の通信シグナルの一部を機械が受信したものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.96,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前たちは一体何なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしてユーを呑み込んだの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:06.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々が呑んだのはその人間が持っていた小型機械だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ホントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:13.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,古代の機械には　小型でも高エネルギーを持っているものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:25.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は熱的に不安定な物質を取り込み
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:30.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,体内で分解して　より静的な状態に安定させる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:53.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この処理が終わった時　地球は生命の長い営みを終えて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,再び眠りにつくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:58.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,その時　我々も眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この都市での活動はほとんど終えた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,都市の武器を全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて都市はゆっくりと停止してゆくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,停止って？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:15.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は最上層以外ほとんどの場所を観測しているが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:20.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,現在生きている人間は君たち二人しか知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:33.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,その子を届けてくれて　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちは群れで行動する必要がある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでヌコがびびってるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前はいいな　仲間がたくさんいて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さよなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:47.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,地球終わるんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:48.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:15.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,世界が終わろうと　どうでもいいことだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私とユーがいれば　それでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:29.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:36.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この歌声　あいつらのものだったんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:36.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっと絶望と仲良くなったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:44.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから悲しげなんだ　終わりの歌だから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:46.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,せーの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:25.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食堂に缶詰があって良かったね　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,また二人だね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:36.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これまでも　これからも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人だけど寂しい？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんが寂しいんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私はユーが寂しいかと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,またまたー　素直じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は寂しくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,行くぞ　早く乗れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あーい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,で　どこへ行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,一番上に決まってるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:20.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね　上に何があろうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:23.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何もないかもしれないけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこに階層があるから登るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:28.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:32.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さて　どっちから行くかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっち
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:51.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,風の吹くまま　それも悪くないな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだ　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,一番上に行ったらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:06.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そしたらその次は月に行こうよ　月に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:07.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:10.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,行こうって言ったのちーちゃんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.01,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:15.31,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　月か　それもいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:16.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,約束だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:17.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,先不说那些莫名其妙的机器
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:40.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这种地方倒还挺整洁的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.23,0:00:43.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为一直是封闭的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.27,0:00:50.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我还以为只要来这种地方 就能知道些以前的事呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.60,0:00:53.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前的事？比如说？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.68,0:00:58.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,比如以前的人是怎么生活的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再比如他们穿什么 说什么语言
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.16,0:01:03.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么你会想知道这些呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,话说 锚不见了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.65,0:01:18.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊 它偶尔会到处乱跑
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是不是又在吃炸弹了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.44,0:01:25.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你很在意吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.79,0:01:29.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们有时不是会遇上别人 然后变成三人行吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.24,0:01:32.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你是指见到石井和金泽那会？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.59,0:01:37.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,锚在的时候也一样 多一个人气氛就会变好不少
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,会变得更热闹
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只有两个人的时候你很寂寞？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.94,0:01:44.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你呢 你会觉得寂寞吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.11,0:01:49.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 有点吧 但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看这包装 感觉里面应该是…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有那东西的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.12,0:02:03.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那东西？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.21,0:02:07.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.23,0:02:12.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的能吃吗 看起来好黑
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能吃的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.03,0:02:16.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是能吃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.68,0:02:27.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这就是那个 巧克力的味道吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.96,0:02:43.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有关食物的事你倒是记得很清楚啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.06,0:02:51.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没准 这就是巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不 应该只是巧克力味的某种食物吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.99,0:02:55.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.57,0:03:04.11,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 这应该也算是过去的事情吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我想 味道也是信息的一种
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,虽然没法记录下来
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 茄…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.40,0:03:18.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,屏幕上出现了文字
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可以连接
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 锚
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.21,0:03:48.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 这些是我们之前拍的照片
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.12,0:03:52.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是把照相机里的内容全显示出来了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,而且是在空中？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,竟然还有这种功能
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 快看 好怀念啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这才过了多久啊 有什么好怀念的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这些照片
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是我们拍的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 看这个
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是画地图的人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,人家叫金泽
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,他…他旁边的女孩是谁啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.25,0:04:33.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这些照片 都是金泽拍的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,和我们认识的时候 他明明是一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.71,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有很多 文件夹
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,文件夹？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,全看一遍吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,全部都能打开
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.63,0:05:06.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好厉害 居然有这么多人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.96,0:05:11.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这些全部都是照相机里的内容吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,动起来了 说话了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这…这就是所谓的视频吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,机器进化论研究会
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,第十二次报告 现在开始
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.98,0:05:34.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,在拍吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,OK OK
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯 这次的样本是这个小型机器
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.87,0:05:46.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们将它命名为17号乙种机器
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.26,0:05:52.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这种机器能够通过往生产设备中添加某种程序
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,强行实现自我繁殖
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是和我们差不多岁数的女孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.26,TEXT-CN-UP 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,很难想象
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.30,0:06:03.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,如此复杂的过程是通过变异和淘汰产生的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是说好要把这理解为机器的进化吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,毕竟 人为的设计应该不会这么利己
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.31,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦 是这样的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这点是很重要的好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.80,0:06:19.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.32,0:06:26.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我好像有点明白 你为什么想知道以前的事情了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那个 我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们一直都是两个人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.57,0:06:48.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但一旦知道以前的人都是这样生活的…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快看 小绿 我是爸爸哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,她在说她讨厌爸爸
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.28,0:07:20.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,给我放尊重点
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,给我放手
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,波奇 过来
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,今日 我国向邻国宣战
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.67,0:07:39.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那么 我们就等综合好意见之后再报告吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我根本没这么说过
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,大规模空袭…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你看 都怪爸爸
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.68,0:08:08.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我军取得大胜 邻国共损失5亿人口
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,于是 我买了薯条回来
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没想到你这么贪吃
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,通知 即将使用电磁波炸弹
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所有的电子设备都将无法使用
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.11,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,第一名是美希
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,祝你生…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,与各城市 各楼层的通讯全数中断
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.08,0:08:58.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,主啊 请允许那些前往天国的兄弟们
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,与您共享永恒的快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就会稍稍觉得不那么寂寞了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能穿过废管堆放场的就只有你们了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,到上层去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.23,0:09:40.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你们的话 靠着不多的粮食也能活很久
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,爷爷你呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,锚又不见了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.39,0:10:14.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,它到底是什么生物呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能开门 能操纵机器
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.56,0:10:23.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还能通过接收器说话
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,算了 管它呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 你到底跑…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有点大啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦 锚？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,得…得追上去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你也会吃掉我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.47,0:11:36.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没有接收器你就没法讲话吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你能想办法和那个大家伙沟通吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能拜托它把小尤吐出来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能听懂我说的话吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.99,0:12:11.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你只是还小 长大后说不定也是人类的敌人
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,敌人…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,什么是敌人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.28,0:13:10.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.71,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我这就过去
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤不在的话 我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没事吧 你都被吃掉了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,稍微努力一下就出来了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,努力一下…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.48,0:15:10.01,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们不会吃掉活生生的人类
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这个声音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是这家伙在讲话吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们没有发声器官
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.61,0:15:20.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但是可以将声波解读为语言
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以 我们借用了这艘船的设备
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幼体的通讯范围十分有限
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以偶尔会发生这种事
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这首歌…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.44,0:15:55.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是机器在接收到我们的部分信号后发出的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.96,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你们到底是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么要把小尤吞下去
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.86,0:16:06.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们吞掉的是那个人类身上的小型机器
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 真的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.65,0:16:13.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有些古代机器虽小 但也蕴含着大量能量
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.37,0:16:25.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们吸收热不稳定物质
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.58,0:16:30.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,在体内分解 使其成为更稳定的物质
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.95,0:16:53.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,处理完毕后 地球的漫长生命将迎来终结
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再次进入休眠
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.27,0:16:58.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那时我们也会沉睡
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们已基本完成应在这座城市中开展的工作
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,城市里的武器全被吞了？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这座城市也将逐渐停止运转
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,停止？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.76,0:17:15.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们一直在观察顶层以外的所有楼层
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.82,0:17:20.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,据我们所知 目前还活着的就只有你们两个
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.77,0:17:33.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们把它送过来
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们需要群体行动
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么锚会害怕啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你真幸福啊 有这么多伙伴
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.36,0:18:47.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,它说地球会进入休眠
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.17,0:18:48.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.86,0:19:15.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就算世界末日来了 对我们来说也无所谓
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只要我们还在一起 就够了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.00,0:19:29.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.65,0:19:36.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原来是它们在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.24,0:19:36.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,绝望估计已经是它们的老朋友了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.73,0:19:44.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以听着才会觉得那么悲伤 毕竟是首末日之歌
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.84,0:19:46.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.04,0:20:25.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幸好食堂里还有些罐头啊 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,又只剩我们两个了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.36,0:20:36.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前是这样 以后也不会变
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这样你很寂寞？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,寂寞的是你吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我是怕你会寂寞
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,又来了 一点都不坦率
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我一点都不寂寞哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为有你在
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要走了 快上车
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那么 我们要去哪？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,当然是去顶层
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.52,0:21:20.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也是啊 先不管上面会有些什么
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.52,0:21:23.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,说不定什么都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只要还没到顶 我们就得继续爬
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.42,0:21:28.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.47,0:21:32.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好了 该往哪边走呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.88,0:21:51.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,迎风向前 这样也不错
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,对了 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,等我们爬到了顶层
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.18,0:22:06.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,接下来就去月亮吧 去月亮
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.65,0:22:07.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,月亮？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.77,0:22:10.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是你自己说要去的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.01,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说过吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.67,0:22:15.31,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 去月亮似乎也不错
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.44,0:22:16.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那说好了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.72,0:22:17.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
